snippet.title: Battle Spirits: Heroes Soul - PSP Gameplay (PPSSPP) 1080p
snippet.description:
In case you wanna help out with the videos: https://www.patreon.com/emulatoruniverse

Battle Spirits Heroes Soul (バトルスピリッツ ヒーローズ ソウル) was the second Battle Spirits game released for the PSP console. It was released March 11, 2010
The game is an RPG, and has no relation to any of the anime series.

Subscribe for more PPSSPP videos and other emulators.
